prompts.recommend_coordination:
Given these clothing items, suggest 3 best outfit combinations.

Available items:
{items_list}

Return ONLY JSON:
{
  "combinations": [
    {
      "name": "Business Casual",
      "itemIds": ["item_id_1", "item_id_2", "item_id_3"],
      "reason": "Why this combination works (max 30 words)",
      "occasion": "office|meeting|casual|formal|date|outdoor|etc"
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
- Each combination must have at least top + bottom (+ shoes if available)
- Consider color harmony and style compatibility
- Return strict JSON only, no markdown, no explanation
